# Decentralized Community Governance Smart Contract
A comprehensive voting platform for decentralized community decision-making built on the Stacks blockchain. This smart contract enables transparent, stake-based governance with weighted voting mechanisms.

##  Features
- **Stake-Based Proposal Creation**: Community members must stake STX to create proposals
- **Weighted Voting System**: Voting power can be customized based on member verification and roles
- **Transparent Governance**: All votes and outcomes are recorded on-chain
- **Administrative Controls**: Built-in emergency procedures and system management
- **Time-Bound Voting**: Configurable voting periods with automatic expiration
- **Comprehensive Tracking**: Detailed records of all governance activities

